Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------正文--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:50.02,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}邻家的南先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:01.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近冬马总是回来得很晚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.94,0:02:03.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.45,0:02:05.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这丫头也有自己的交际圈子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:08.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从新交了个叫作「千秋」的朋友才这样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.92,0:02:09.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像和咱家一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.04,0:02:11.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姓氏是「南」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.61,0:02:17.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但愿别是个不好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.23,0:02:20.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马要晚些回来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.19,0:02:23.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边可是很周到地打电话来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.43,0:02:25.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.42,0:02:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来这阵子嘴巴倒是更刻薄了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.88,0:02:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有些男孩子气了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.37,0:02:33.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成天对着没出息的哥哥们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.82,0:02:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是就比别人更加男孩子气了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.65,0:02:37.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才那番话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.62,0:02:40.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把自己也算进去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.75,0:02:41.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.88,0:02:45.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄不好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.48,0:02:48.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有心仪的男孩子了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:53.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有喜欢的男孩不该是更有女人味儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.01,0:02:57.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对家人变得冷淡也挺正常的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.82,0:03:00.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的南家似乎有三个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:02.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄不好有个帅气的大哥哥之类
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.10,0:03:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.35,0:03:12.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这帅气的大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱家就已经够多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.69,0:03:16.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞎说什么呢  大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.70,0:03:18.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟着冬马一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.01,0:03:20.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去南家调查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.57,0:03:22.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？让我去？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.53,0:03:23.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:25.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边留冬马吃了好几回饭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.75,0:03:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱们好歹也得表示一下谢意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:30.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿礼数作障眼法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:32.67,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（翌日）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:36.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天哥哥跟我一起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.47,0:03:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让他先在外头等着了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.76,0:03:42.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说  你家也真够呛的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.68,0:03:44.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可受了不少罪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.32,0:03:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来春香似乎心情很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.99,0:03:53.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么看他们都是认为咱家不可信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.13,0:03:56.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  你有没有认真在听
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.89,0:04:01.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说电话里我那尖嗓子很可疑？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.43,0:04:03.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  刚才说的那些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.56,0:04:06.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说冬马家很有意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.12,0:04:07.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在外头等着的那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:11.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放他进来你哥哥们也就不会再担无谓的心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.00,0:04:14.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是冬马的哥哥秋良
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.19,0:04:17.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妹妹一直以来承蒙你们照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.29,0:04:19.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点小意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真够小意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.38,0:04:31.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为凭几块肥皂就可以打发我们了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这大谈特谈少女心的三少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.23,0:04:35.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马  你都说了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.98,0:04:37.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么就说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.47,0:04:40.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱大姐头的心情可不会因为几块肥皂就好起…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.25,0:04:43.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  好像变好了些…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:49.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道冬马在这儿过得怎么样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.50,0:04:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就像对待冬马一样来招待你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.48,0:04:53.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  大姐头
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.24,0:04:55.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你改作盘腿坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.24,0:04:55.97,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（注：较正式的场合为跪坐）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.03,0:04:57.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是命令哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:04:58.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.04,0:05:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和冬马一起留下来吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.49,0:05:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我吃得丁点儿不剩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.01,0:05:04.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.10,0:05:07.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得我们都姓南
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好好相处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.96,0:05:11.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你小子知道知道谁比较配姓南
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没说这话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.66,0:05:22.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进展是否顺利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.94,0:05:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来电话了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.13,0:05:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好  这里是南家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:32.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是南冬马家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:33.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是南千秋的姐姐南春香
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.24,0:05:40.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马君和秋良君在我这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.35,0:05:42.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.71,0:05:45.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.39,0:05:47.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  这调子也太低沉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:48.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.98,0:05:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是绑架
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:55.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.53,0:05:56.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.10,0:05:58.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  喂喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.76,0:05:59.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.05,0:06:01.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.71,0:06:09.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么扯到这个话题的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.17,0:06:12.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你说自己无论如何都想要个女人的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.68,0:06:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过这话？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.01,0:06:17.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  我开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:18.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩笑？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:20.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你还真说中了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.47,0:06:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说中了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.53,0:06:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我常常想怎么样才能有个女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.90,0:06:31.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数学课之类的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.50,0:06:33.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会很认真地思考这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.27,0:06:36.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要看看我的数学笔记？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不错的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.23,0:06:42.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像上面写满了令人生厌的秋良方程式
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,π等于2h
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.27,0:06:49.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  呃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.35,0:06:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来谈谈你喜欢的类型吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.23,0:06:54.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.90,0:06:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了夏奈  随便是谁都行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.72,0:07:00.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.84,0:07:01.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事你得先明白我对你没有意思再说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我按顺序来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:09.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我弄错顺序了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.63,0:07:10.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.23,0:07:13.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家春香怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.34,0:07:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错是不错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她给我的第一印象是恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.99,0:07:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  那一头长发倒是不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:33.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那儿有个正合适的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.67,0:07:46.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤冈君的小白脸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:48.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那男人是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.64,0:07:50.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去和南同学关系不错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:52.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他俩到底是什么关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.12,0:07:56.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  若无其事地和南同学搭话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.13,0:07:58.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若～无其事地问他们的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.34,0:07:59.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若无其事地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.30,0:08:00.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若无其事地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你喜欢的类型了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.86,0:08:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要交给本小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.92,0:08:14.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.38,0:08:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像气势汹汹地瞪着我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.61,0:08:20.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈同学  那是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:22.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  说他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.71,0:08:24.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠太近了靠太近了靠太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.03,0:08:26.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是头儿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:28.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头…头儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.66,0:08:30.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚下功夫相当了得哦  那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.57,0:08:41.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会…会被踹死的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:47.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？这氛围不对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.83,0:08:49.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若无其事地走过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却不能若无其事地搭话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.54,0:08:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是刚才那位黑发美女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:08:59.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.46,0:09:02.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是头儿的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.12,0:09:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我盯着她看得出神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.80,0:09:06.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以头儿不乐意了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:08.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您不必担心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.96,0:09:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会对别人的女朋友下手的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:12.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.37,0:09:12.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.33,0:09:16.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说的话我还是喜欢夏奈同学这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.69,0:09:20.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就先这么着了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.95,0:09:28.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.03,0:09:31.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你那些话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说要和我比试比试对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.64,0:09:36.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.42,0:09:45.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能告诉我你的班级和名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.78,0:09:49.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您放过我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:53.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤冈君难得一见的神情的小白脸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋良那家伙最近没什么精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:06.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是上次来咱家的冬马的哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:08.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是学校里有什么事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.99,0:10:12.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  看我让他振作起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:14.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:16.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.69,0:10:18.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:19.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啊来啊  笑一个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.81,0:10:20.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好笑的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好笑的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.76,0:10:26.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑一个笑一个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.61,0:10:27.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小白脸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.70,0:10:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小白脸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:30.54,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…很有意思的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:33.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小白脸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.58,0:10:32.03,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.12,0:10:34.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:36.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.71,0:10:37.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Byebye
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.06,0:10:41.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.68,0:11:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字就叫山田了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.18,0:11:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.79,0:11:23.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  那还真是了不得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.71,0:11:24.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:25.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.55,0:11:31.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加把劲儿  山田
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:33.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快到顶了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.57,0:11:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后啊  我家那口子就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.31,0:12:02.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别吓我  蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.86,0:12:13.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  山田
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:22.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.11,0:12:31.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最后一道关口  山田
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.38,0:12:33.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.58,0:12:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得漂亮  山田
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:47.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.01,0:12:53.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  山田
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.32,0:12:55.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀嗬  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.49,0:12:57.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先下脚为强
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.50,0:13:09.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.69,0:13:11.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.53,0:13:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.85,0:13:23.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:26.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食欲魔人千秋大人居然吃不下饭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.35,0:13:28.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.81,0:13:33.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田他坐卡车走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.19,0:13:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转学？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.18,0:13:38.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了啦  人生正所谓聚散离合嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:40.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不都因为你  蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:41.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:42.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.70,0:13:44.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  你做了什么是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:46.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还莫名其妙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我压根儿就不认识什么山田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.65,0:13:49.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:52.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真不认识
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.26,0:13:53.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山田
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.09,0:14:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来打排球吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:23.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二哥夏树原本挺好动的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.64,0:14:27.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从参加社团活动之后就老实多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.86,0:14:29.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要再来一碗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.39,0:14:30.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  有劳了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:32.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得好像是排球部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.17,0:14:34.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说他总是挺早回家的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:36.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋良
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.46,0:14:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是来接冬马的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.35,0:14:41.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么自己都吃得这么带劲儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.81,0:14:44.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许再添一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.92,0:14:49.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏树
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.22,0:14:52.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保坂学长好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.62,0:14:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.75,0:14:56.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天能参加练习了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.80,0:14:57.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.40,0:15:00.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天得回去做饭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:01.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.16,0:15:04.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来  这是我做的便当
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.98,0:15:05.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你尝尝看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.12,0:15:06.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:08.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别误会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.42,0:15:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道这便当是否配得上我最爱的女子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.54,0:15:13.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以让你尝尝味道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:15.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.77,0:15:17.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真吓了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.11,0:15:20.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给女生做便当能让她开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.34,0:15:22.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该能的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.67,0:15:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.07,0:15:26.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚吃过饭  现在还饱着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.05,0:15:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不可能说得上什么感受
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.91,0:15:32.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些不是你的午餐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:35.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是留着待会儿吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.32,0:15:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留着待会儿吃的不能现在打开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.47,0:15:41.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.93,0:15:44.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能现在吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.27,0:15:46.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:50.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不知道女生喜欢什么味道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.18,0:15:53.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么不了解女生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.48,0:15:56.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把女生视为未知的生物一般
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.15,0:16:00.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏树真是座冰山
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.10,0:16:08.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.60,0:16:10.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又整出个怪里怪气的喽啰来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.79,0:16:18.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏树  你来二年级的教室有事儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.03,0:16:23.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我弟弟妹妹承蒙南春香同学款待
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.22,0:16:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以过来打个招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.56,0:16:28.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是个挺重视礼仪的家伙嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.12,0:16:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香在那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.77,0:16:39.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.13,0:16:42.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也来参加社团活动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.91,0:16:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.62,0:16:48.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  有人找你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.39,0:16:48.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.70,0:16:51.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,排球部的男生很悲惨的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.98,0:16:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得有人告诉保坂学长罚跑操场50圈是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:16:59.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我得回家做饭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.68,0:17:02.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是找春香有事儿对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.30,0:17:04.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.20,0:17:11.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春…春香…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:19.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.31,0:17:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.15,0:17:23.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.13,0:17:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以大概知道是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然众目睽睽之下很难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:29.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至想现在就跑开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.12,0:17:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不做个了断的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.01,0:17:34.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱俩彼此都不痛快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.52,0:17:35.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.77,0:17:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.38,0:17:47.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我试试味儿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.83,0:17:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芋头栗子和松菇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.33,0:17:54.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很有秋天的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.91,0:17:57.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这样香味就不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.15,0:17:59.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏树？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.65,0:18:01.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.49,0:18:03.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有血的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.75,0:18:05.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得多吸收铁质
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.77,0:18:14.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐菜刀的声音乱了分寸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:15.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是出什么事儿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.10,0:18:17.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么夏树
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:23.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在学校见到春香了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.06,0:18:25.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见倒是见到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:28.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却惹出麻烦来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.86,0:18:30.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.65,0:18:31.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事儿了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:41.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天放学之后我去千秋家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.40,0:18:42.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.37,0:18:45.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在听我说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.71,0:18:52.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.07,0:18:54.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  冬马
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.22,0:19:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  春香  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.28,0:19:07.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马  借这个机会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.43,0:19:08.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.05,0:19:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实春香算是很懒的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:14.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是在犯懒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:17.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没人让她提起精神来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.54,0:19:19.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是相当懒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.73,0:19:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天春香是最早回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:30.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香当时是这么想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.03,0:19:32.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「先睡一觉吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.15,0:19:36.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不过还是先换衣服再睡吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.49,0:19:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「算了算了」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.43,0:19:41.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「太麻烦了  就这么睡吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:48.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道她是这么想的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:50.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:57.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三颗扣子半扣半开的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.70,0:19:58.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.79,0:20:00.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想解开却又放弃了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.31,0:20:07.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我二哥想来和你们打个招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.62,0:20:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.40,0:20:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是早说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.87,0:20:10.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他现在在外头
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.99,0:20:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去叫他进来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.75,0:20:13.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.16,0:20:15.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不礼貌的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:18.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是冬马的哥哥夏树
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.51,0:20:20.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前些天真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.98,0:20:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妹妹承蒙你平日的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.05,0:20:25.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  这样很不礼貌的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.52,0:20:26.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.46,0:20:44.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请抬起头来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你是那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.09,0:20:53.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你是冬马的哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.30,0:20:55.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连这你都没告诉人家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.63,0:20:57.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  前些天的事情不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.07,0:20:59.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请抬起头来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.54,0:21:02.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在听我说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.17,0:21:04.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不是很不礼貌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.12,0:21:09.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许你也有失礼之处人家才不好抬起头来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.11,0:21:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种程度的身体接触就动手确实有些过分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.84,0:21:15.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是吓了一跳…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.87,0:21:17.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是高中生了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.46,0:21:19.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在创造传说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.30,0:21:20.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.73,0:21:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐  衣服  衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:30.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不告诉我？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.13,0:21:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我若无其事地提醒过你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.37,0:21:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.19,0:21:34.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏树的旧伤又发作了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.09,0:21:37.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.80,0:21:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抬起头来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.02,0:21:46.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,止不住血  止不住血
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.72,0:21:47.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏树
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.47,0:21:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就帮你止血  不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.02,0:21:50.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快擦干  快擦干
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.56,0:21:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐  衣服  衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.72,0:21:55.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位观众  要多吸收铁质哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.74,0:21:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～  我也想去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集预告
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.92,0:23:33.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长  下次是圣诞节的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.40,0:23:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.09,0:23:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说让我去扮作南春香的圣诞老人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.49,0:23:40.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此  得先准备上乘的服装和驯鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.42,0:23:42.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向一流的圣诞老人看齐…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.00,0:23:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  圣诞节啊圣诞夜啊
